name: Few early postings for nrKe
description: consider this... its like an Album shop where you can look in the store and play the songs but if you wish have legal permission to copy play make up your own compilations, even sync to NFT you have to pay 1 tez for this album NFT which has the rights contract contained. Of course there is only 1000 copies which may make these NFT's collectable in the future. The rights to the music listed within the NFT is granted to the NFT owner for as long as he/she owns the album NFT. With the sale of the NFT the rights pass to the new owner. Songs can just be downloaded from recordshop. links are in the tags
